ered stems from the\nexistence of the single non-analytic change of the eigenstates of the clean\nmany-body Hamiltonian at the equilibrium melting transition present in low\nenergy solid-type eigenstates. We derive a single (possibly computable)\ndimensionless parameter fit to the viscosity and suggest other testable\npredictions of our approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Oct 2015 20:18:06 GMT"},{"version":"v10","created":"Mon, 9 May 2016 19:55:30 GMT"},{"version":"v11","created":"Tue, 10 May 2016 18:17:44 GMT"},{"version":"v12","created":"Wed, 11 May 2016 19:44:55 GMT"},{"version":"v13","created":"Tue, 17 May 2016 15:14:35 GMT"},{"version":"v14","created":"Fri, 24 Jun 2016 02:00:47 GMT"},{"version":"v15","created":"Thu, 8 Sep 2016 19:52:27 GMT"},{"version":"v16","created":"Mon, 12 Sep 2016 18:51:27 GMT"},{"version":"v17","created":"Tue, 13 Sep 2016 15:33:20 GMT"},{"version":"v18","created":"Fri, 30 Sep 2016 18:52:06 GMT"},{"version":"v19","created":"Thu, 15 Dec 2016 09:56:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Dec 2015 19:23:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 9 Dec 2015 18:12:29 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2015 20:55:51 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 19 Apr 2016 19:57:28 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Mon, 2 May 2016 16:54:43 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Tue, 3 May 2016 15:03:55 GMT"},{"version":"v8","created":"Thu, 5 May 2016 17:27:27 GMT"},{"version":"v9","created":"Fri, 6 May 2016 16:52:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-16"}
