 in\n$O(n\\cdot \\log(n)\\cdot m)$ steps. Also, we derive several new\nErd\\H{o}s-P\\'osa-type results from the techniques that we introduce.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 14 Oct 2015 01:41:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 19 Jan 2017 21:44:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-23"}
