perated in a\nmanner such that the correlation signal remains unaffected by the additional\nnonlinear terms. We also show how such a practical STC can be realized using a\ncombination of a porous-glass based Rb vapor cell, a holographic video disc,\nand a lithium niobate crystal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Oct 2015 17:53:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 25 Oct 2015 08:23:41 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 28 Nov 2015 21:06:07 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 15 Jan 2016 20:28:00 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Wed, 6 Apr 2016 13:47:40 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2016 20:20:51 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Sun, 1 May 2016 02:06:08 GMT"},{"version":"v8","created":"Tue, 10 May 2016 20:57:52 GMT"},{"version":"v9","created":"Sun, 5 Jun 2016 23:48:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-24"}
