y) natal kicks for massive BHs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Oct 2015 20:12:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2016 17:05:38 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 27 Mar 2016 16:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-06"}
